<p>The online post quickly received more than 1,500 'likes' from other shoppers who were amazed with the budget buy.</p>

<p>'How good do these look!' one woman said.</p>

<p>'I'm so getting myself some of these,' another said.</p>

<p>A third added: 'My son's room is full of IKEA! Kmart why do you do this to me? Damn Kmart could of saved me so much!'</p>

<p>Others praised the simple but stylish design and said they'll definitely be heading to Kmart soon to purchase the product themselves before it sells out. </p>
